> 30 June - Ministry of Industry was established
> 2 July - Osman Bolukbası, the chairman of Republican Nation Party was arrested
> 25 September - Operation Deep Water, a big NATO exercise around Canakkale.
> 27 October - General elections (DP 419 seats, CHP 173 seats CMP 4 seats, HP 4 seats)
> 20 October - Yarimburgaz train disaster, the worst train accident with 95 dead and 150 wounded people 
> 25 November - Ministry of Tourism was established
> 28 November - Liberty Party (HP) was merged to Republican People’s Party (CHP)